latestPosts.caption:
Literally it was the longest month so far, I started off with being the most productive person ever to being bed rotten by end of the month. Haha! 
Lots of interesting things happened and deep and long talks with my people, I talked my heart out this month with people in my circle. 

Also on the note of Romanticising my Life- 
- took myself out on a Date
- Gave a fresh cut to my hair 
- stopped doing my nails and I let it breathe for this month, felt nice. 
- Outing with my frndz, met lots of new cats, Danced on K-pop songs. 
- while maintaining my work and studies side by side, Pheww!!! 

Journal entry Done :- 30/3/2025

#monthlydump
